  line `THE SCHEDULE`
  line `( See s ection 2)`
  line `1. Fruit.`
  line `2. Vegetables.`
  line `3. Eggs.`
  line `4. Dairy produce.`
  line `5. Tobacco.`
  line `6. Coffee.`
  line `7. Hides and Skins.`
  line `8. Fruit products.`
  line `9. Atta.`
  line `10. Oilseeds.`
  line `11. Vegetable oils (including hydrogenated oils and vegetable fats).`
  line `12. Cotton.`
  line `13. Rice.`
  line `14. Lac.`
  line `15. Wheat`
  line `16. Sann Hemp.`
  line `17. Sugarcane gur (Jaggery).`
  line `18. Myrobalans.`
  line `19. Bura.`
  line `20. Wool and Goat Hair.`
  line `21. Bristles.`
  line `22. Rosin and Turpentine.`
  line `23. Arecanuts.`
  line `24. Essential Oil.`
  line `25. Cashew nut.`
  line `26. Cardamom.`
  line `27. Pepper.`
  line `28. Ginger.`
  line `29. Honey.`
  line `30. Curry Powder.`
  line `31. Kapok.`
